The Neutron Star Launcher
Replaces Pyrophobia

The first nova will kill you, the smaller novas following the first can kill an enemy, granting you a second wind
UPDATE: lowered blast radius, so you wouldn't kill yourself when using this
Extremely high damage
Consumes 10 ammo per shot
High blast radius
Slows movement speed
Slow ammo regeneration
Releases supernovas non stop

Recommended weapon code:  BL2(hwAAAABSGABEx4I/ECGTVaIYQ/GJQgAFG4r///////+Dovj/r4ri)

